                    <h2>PORTFOLIO</h2>
                    <p>A portfolio project is a collection of projects and programs that are managed as a
                        <br> group to achieve strategic objectives12. A portfolio can be managed at either
                        <br> the functional or the organizational level. A portfolio is used to structure 
                        <br>and manage investments and to optimize strategic benefits or operational efficiency</p>
                </div>
            </div>
